6. React JS Tutorial 06

https://github.com/acdlite/react-fiber-architecture

What is reconcillation ?
What is virtual DOM?
Latest approach of Fibre?

Reconciliation	: Process of comparing Virtual DOMs and updating the real DOM

Virtual DOM	: Lightweight copy of real DOM for faster diffing

React first creates a Virtual DOM version of this element.

Then it checks if it needs to update anything.

If yes, it updates the Real DOM — and that’s what appears in the browser.

Fiber	: New rendering system that supports pausing/resuming work for better performance

